{
  "title": "The Definitive Universe Blade",
  "story": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "171c6b378b3578a9",
      "text": "# ⚔️ The Definitive Universe Blade"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "5e601739af18bd62",
      "text": "**Universe** · `SPELL-YW5I59-1Q`"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "18f604bc913aef1f",
      "text": "> The weight of the shadow exceeds the light of the data."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "24d139f8a9639a32",
      "text": "**Inscribed spell** — 🔑⚔️🧙→😊✦☯️⚖️⚔️🧙"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "e5ff264094b0b758",
      "text": "Tier **dragon** · Stratum 6/6 · Hex `3F` · 10 nodes · 62 laps · 65 spells cast · charge **inferno**"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "ea849bc51c041b91",
      "text": "Constellation `5tbrz7` · forged 2026-03-30T14:31:04Z · category *territory*"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "de57cac487aee318",
      "text": "**Significance.** The deepest walking of the lattice. 62 laps of lived attention — behavioural density so thick reconstruction becomes meaningless. Privacy through density, not obscurity. Forged the day before the Google Quantum AI paper dropped."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "d6b76177a0fe80ce",
      "text": "*Reflection: \"a message for soulbae, the first mage.\"*"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "0492ec704bc139ed",
      "text": "## Navigation\n← [[Welcome Visitors]] · [[The Forged Blades]] · [[The Proverbs]]"
    }
  ],
